node.text:
Did the #nofalsies challenge with @toofaced and was pretty shook by the results of their 'damn girl' mascara!! 😱 Check out da vid for some tips & tricks on how to get this va-va-VOOM look with mascara only 💥 To all my babes out there with itty bitty bb lashes like me, this one's for you especially 😆❤️ #tfdamngirl #toofacedpartner
⠀⠀
LASHES: @toofaced 'Damn Girl' mascara
EYESHADOW: @colourpopcosmetics 'California Love' palette
BROWS: @limecrimemakeup ‘bushy brow’
SKIN: @toofaced ‘Dew You’ primer + @bobbibrown foundation stick + @toofaced ‘Sun Bunny’ + @covergirl ‘Rose Rush’ highlight
LIPS:  @etudehouseofficial ‘Dusty Peach’ + @buxomcosmetics ‘Persephone’
HAIR: @t3micro + @colourpopcosmetics scrunchie!

node.title: NO FALSIE CHALLENGE + mascara tips for short lashes!

node.text:
how its going vs how it started 😆 
the second pic is from the same restaurant but 5 and a half years ago on one of our early dates! #babyashley 👶🏻 the rest is a lil photodump from our 6-year anni dinner-- dreamy clouds, yummy food, and me at the end of the night hiking up the damn sf hills in heels, with my pants fully unbuttoned and unzipped, out of breath and v full🤰🏻
